ch.cern.dbod.db.entity

Class CommandParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.cern.dbod.db.entity.CommandParam

  • public class CommandParam
extends Object
    Represents a parameter job that has to be carried out on a database. In the parameters we include things like the timestamp for a recovery, the config file to upload, etc.
    Author:
    Daniel Gomez Blanco
